exercises.instructions:
Simulate breaking change detection workflow:
1. ConsumerV1: expects {paymentId, status}
2. ConsumerV2 (after Razorpay breaks API): expects same but API returns {id, state}
3. Show: V2 test fails because provider broke contract
4. Demonstrate: how CI gate (can-i-deploy logic) works
5. @SpringBootTest (2 tests): V1 passes, V2 fails (and we verify it fails correctly)

